1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ The howling wind ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 14 =

20
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,139
Hang in there.

21
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:39,109
Yes.

22
00:01:44,059 --> 00:01:44,800
Push.

23
00:01:45,784 --> 00:01:46,486
Push.

24
00:01:48,855 --> 00:01:50,483
- Gauze.- Here you are.

25
00:01:50,883 --> 00:01:51,606
Give me the water.

26
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:52,820
Okay.

27
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,836
Get another pot of water.

28
00:01:54,726 --> 00:01:55,387
Madam,

29
00:01:56,389 --> 00:01:57,106
push.

30
00:01:58,306 --> 00:01:59,669
Come on, push.

31
00:01:59,993 --> 00:02:00,918
Madam,

32
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,114
Madam.

33
00:02:06,469 --> 00:02:07,436
Almost done.

34
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:10,180
Push.

35
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,826
Hang in there, Madam.

36
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,340
What’s wrong?

37
00:02:18,020 --> 00:02:19,420
The pain started the day before yesterday.

38
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:21,020
Why she’s still struggling?

39
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:23,260
Is she having a difficult labor?

40
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,460
No, it can’t be.

41
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:28,140
The baby is in the perfect position.

42
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:29,860
Almost done.

43
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,540
I can see the hair.

44
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:34,100
Your Majesty,

45
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,180
Your Majesty, take the medicine first.

46
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,540
You’ve been staying here for two days.

47
00:02:42,740 --> 00:02:44,260
The anxiety attacks your heart
and you caught a cold.

48
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,420
Now you are having a fever.

49
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:47,540
If it becomes serious,

50
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:50,540
Madam Miao will feel guilty about it.

51
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:54,380
Come on.

52
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:04,820
Relax,

53
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,060
physician said it’s not a difficult labor.

54
00:03:07,540 --> 00:03:08,300
It is common

55
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:10,740
to take two or three days for the first baby.

56
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:12,380
People say

57
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:13,940
the baby that takes longer

58
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,740
must be a clever boy or a beautiful girl.

59
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,900
= Liang Yuanheng =
Mr. Zhang.

60
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,740
Come on, I’ll take you to Her Highness.

61
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:01,900
Don’t be afraid.

62
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:03,580
You are lucky.

63
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,500
Just now the princess was born.

64
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:06,820
The whole palace is bestowed with amnesty.

65
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:40,380
Do you know what you did wrong?

66
00:04:41,460 --> 00:04:42,660
Yes, I know.

67
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,980
It seems that I didn’t avoid the taboo,

68
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:47,540
but my manners show what I think inside of me.

69
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:49,180
I behaved wrong

70
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:51,740
because I didn’t respect enough in my heart.

71
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:54,060
I was raised in countryside

72
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:56,060
in an ungracious and vulgar way.

73
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,420
I didn’t keep royalty to His Majesty

74
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,620
in my mind all the time,

75
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:04,500
that’s why I forgot the taboo.

76
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,300
You do realize something

77
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,660
these days in the reflection.

78
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,980
He looks lovely,

79
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:17,540
clever,

80
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:18,980
and clean.

81
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:20,980
He made a mistake

82
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,140
but with the princess’s birth

83
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:25,540
he’s lucky to have another chance.

84
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:27,460
Maoze,

85
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,100
take him

86
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,820
to change some clean clothes

87
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:32,940
and eat something

88
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:34,740
and give him a bowl of ginger soup.

89
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:37,260
It’s quite cold recently, don’t let him be sick.

90
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:39,860
Yes.

91
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,860
Thank you, Your Highness.

92
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:48,060
Don’t thank me.

93
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:51,060
This is the blessing from the princess.

94
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,780
But your name

95
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,340
is too dangerous,

96
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:02,980
you should change a new one.

97
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,620
Please bestow me a new name, Your Highness.

98
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:10,660
Huaiji.

99
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:16,220
From now on, your name is Liang Huaiji.

100
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:26,900
= Princess Huirou =

101
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,300
Sorry, Your Majesty,

102
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:32,500
I didn’t give you a son.

103
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:36,180
I feel guilty to my ancestors

104
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,900
but deep down in my heart,

105
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:38,980
I feel so happy.

106
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,220
My wish is fulfilled

107
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:43,260
to have a princess I can spoil.

108
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,100
Before long

109
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:45,260
we can still have a son

110
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:46,140
to fulfill our moral obligation to my ancestors.

111
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:49,300
You just want to make me happy.

112
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,020
I’ve been

113
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:53,580
collecting those for more than a year.

114
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:56,140
What are they?

115
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,700
Among all the tributes Suzhou sent

116
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:00,180
to the palace a year ago,

117
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,460
I saw this doll.

118
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:04,660
I was dreaming I can have a princess

119
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:06,900
and give this to her as a gift.

120
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:08,380
Since then,

121
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:09,780
I’ve been longing

122
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:11,060
for a daughter.

123
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:12,460
And soon

124
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:13,860
I heard that you were pregnant.

125
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:17,060
It’s because the Heaven responded to your wish.

126
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:25,540
What a delicate doll.

127
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,100
Will our daughter

128
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,620
like this doll?

129
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:33,100
What if she prefers writing,
painting and calligraphy

130
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:35,500
to dolls and jades?

131
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,780
Then,

132
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:39,020
I collected different kinds of items

133
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:40,620
and after a year,

134
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:41,500
I got

135
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,660
a box of gifts for her.

136
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:50,340
I always think

137
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:52,900
if it’s a boy,

138
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:56,220
I must teach him well

139
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:57,500
and give him the best teacher;

140
00:07:58,460 --> 00:07:59,660
if it’s a girl,

141
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:03,140
I’ll let her be the happiest girl

142
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:04,260
in the whole Song.

143
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,580
I’m Liang Yuansheng,

144
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:17,220
a resident in the Capital.

145
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:18,900
= Liaocheng =
I came here today

146
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:21,980
to appeal for redress of a wrong
and issue a lawsuit.

147
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:24,220
= Liang Yuansheng =
My uncle

148
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:25,300
and my brother were wronged.

149
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:29,140
I want to sue someone in this county.

150
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:33,100
You should go to county government
for redress and lawsuit

151
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,620
and tell the magistrate your case.

152
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:37,660
I want to sue

153
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:40,540
my aunt-in-law

154
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:43,300
and the magistrate of Liaocheng.

155
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:49,220
Even if it’s the magistrate,

156
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:52,060
you still need to go
to the county government and beat the drum.

157
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:53,580
You shouldn’t come to my mansion.

158
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,060
Everyone, leave here!

159
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,380
I know the rules,

160
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:02,220
but I’m left with no choice.

161
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:05,940
I want to sue them for committing adultery

162
00:09:05,940 --> 00:09:06,980
and selling kid.

163
00:09:08,220 --> 00:09:09,140
Adultery needs two people.

164
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:11,300
I’ve tied them up in the bedroom

165
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,900
so everyone can see it

166
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:13,940
and be a witness.

167
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:20,580
How can you hold a government official?

168
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:22,820
Do you know you’ve broken the law?

169
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:25,660
My brother just turned 10 this year

170
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:28,340
and was sold by them.

171
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:30,500
Sir,

172
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:33,180
I just want justice.

173
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:35,180
People who had adultery, who were corrupted,

174
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:36,660
who broke the law

175
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:37,620
and ruined the government’s reputation

176
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:39,140
should be punished with what he deserves.

177
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,420
I...

178
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,460
I will also get

179
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,740
the punishment I deserve.

180
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:54,740
Congratulations, Your Majesty,
for having a princess.

181
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:58,380
The princess

182
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:00,220
is my first child.

183
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:01,820
Today

184
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:03,820
I’ll follow the tradition

185
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:04,980
of the birth of the first imperial son.

186
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:07,060
I’ll bestow all of you the baptism gift

187
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:09,460
so that you can share the joy with me.

188
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,420
It will be sent to your house

189
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:15,980
in the sequence of your names and titles.

190
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,460
= Yin Zhu, courtesy name Shilu =

191
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:30,540
Your Majesty,

192
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:32,580
in my opinion,

193
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:35,020
we have soldiers guarding
our boundaries day and night,

194
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:37,300
people who are struggling for living.

195
00:10:37,660 --> 00:10:40,260
Yet Your Majesty bestowed officials with

196
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,540
jewelry and jade

197
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:43,380
for the birth of a princess.

198
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:44,940
It runs contrary to your normal instructions

199
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:47,300
about encouraging thrift and discouraging luxury.

200
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:49,300
Beside it runs contrary to

201
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,860
the etiquettes

202
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:52,300
to follow the tradition

203
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,380
of the birth of the first imperial son.

204
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:56,340
I beg Your Majesty to recall your decision.

205
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:09,020
The gift

206
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:10,300
is nothing more than

207
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:12,340
some small items in stock,

208
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,660
which didn’t cost anything extra.

209
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,740
If I leave them there,

210
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,340
they’ll continue to be dust collectors.

211
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:21,380
I gave them to you to share my luck and joy.

212
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,100
If you are concerned about

213
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:25,660
soldiers protecting our country,

214
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,740
and the people with a hard life,

215
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:28,860
and you are willing to change your gifts into money

216
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:30,500
and donate it to them

217
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:31,700
so that they can share

218
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:33,540
the luck of the birth

219
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:35,660
and my joy as a new father,

220
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:37,580
that will be terrific.

221
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:40,380
Your Majesty,

222
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:45,140
= Duan Shaolian, courtesy name Xiyi =
I have something important to discuss at the court.

223
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:49,620
It’s 16 years since you are in charge.

224
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:52,460
You are almost 30,

225
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:55,180
but have only one princess.

226
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,340
Prince is the foundation of the country.

227
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:02,300
It is not a usual thing

228
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,900
to have no crown prince for more than 10 years.

229
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:07,180
In 1002 A.D.,

230
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:08,820
after Prince Zhou deceased,

231
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:12,500
the former emperor

232
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,420
took the third son of Prince Shang

233
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,740
back to the palace

234
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:18,100
till you were born.

235
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:22,540
You have only a daughter,

236
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:24,900
you should pick a royal son to be your successor.

237
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:27,260
You are almost 30,

238
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:29,620
but have only a daughter,

239
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:32,940
you should pick a royal son to be your successor.

240
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:55,180
Huirou,

241
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:58,860
you are so cute.

242
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,900
I remember my two nephews

243
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:03,340
at her age

244
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:05,220
could only poke their fingers randomly,

245
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:06,940
and cry if they couldn’t find their mouth.

246
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:10,660
Huirou,

247
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,700
you know I’m praising you?

248
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:14,300
You are smiling at me?

249
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:17,380
Huirou likes Your Highness.

250
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:21,860
Princess knows Your Highness.

251
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:23,500
She didn’t smile at us.

252
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:25,300
His Majesty is here.

253
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:34,940
- Your Majesty.- Your Majesty.

254
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,500
Huirou,

255
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:50,260
all my depression

256
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:52,220
will go away the moment I see you.

257
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:00,820
Nothing.

258
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,580
It’s just some

259
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:05,300
hateful faces and tedious words.

260
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:11,900
Huirou, you are the refreshment to me.

261
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:15,500
Smells so good.

262
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:19,980
I roughly looked through

263
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,500
the tributes from Qiongzhou.

264
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:22,660
Nothing is particularly special

265
00:14:23,220 --> 00:14:25,420
other than two big luminous pearls.

266
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:27,700
Later I’ll let Liaozi to bring them here

267
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:30,220
and put them on Huirou’s bed shelf

268
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:31,700
to bring her some soft light at night

269
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,100
so that when she wakes up at night,

270
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,820
she won’t be sacred by darkness.

271
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,180
Your Majesty,

272
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:40,980
Huirou is just a little girl.

273
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:43,220
Toys and jade items you gave her before

274
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,820
are so many for me.

275
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:48,460
The rare treasure even in tributes

276
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:49,780
is not something she can deserve.

277
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:50,740
What are you talking about?

278
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:52,020
What’s wrong with being a girl?

279
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:56,060
She is my one and only first daughter,

280
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,460
she deserves all the jewelries.

281
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,700
How can a woman

282
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:09,260
compare to your loftiness.

283
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:12,580
All mothers in the world are alike.

284
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:14,380
They always have some inexplicable worries.

285
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:17,260
Especially for Huirou

286
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,180
who has already been

287
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:20,900
the most honorable girl in the world

288
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:21,780
when she’s just a tender baby.

289
00:15:22,260 --> 00:15:23,580
She’s worried it might be too much for her.

290
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:26,260
I feel the same.

291
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:27,940
I am even worried of

292
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,660
hurting her

293
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:32,740
by merely holding her in my arms.

294
00:15:39,140 --> 00:15:42,140
Don’t take the luminous pearls

295
00:15:42,140 --> 00:15:43,500
as some rare treasure.

296
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:44,740
Just take them as some balls

297
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:45,780
that are luminous at night.

298
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,940
They are useless to adults,

299
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:51,220
but if they’re put on Huirou’s bed shelf,

300
00:15:51,220 --> 00:15:53,380
they will gleam some soft lights

301
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:55,060
so that when Huirou wakes up at night,

302
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,420
she won’t just see darkness,

303
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:58,700
and the light won’t disturb her sleep either.

304
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,220
You are very thoughtful, Your Majesty.

305
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:05,260
The pearls are perfect for Huirou.

306
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,980
Your Highness is sensible indeed.

307
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:14,980
Thank you, Your Majesty.

308
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:33,260
Huaiji,

309
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:35,180
Huaiji,

310
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:38,700
did you know

311
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:39,940
Mr. Zhang Maoze before?

312
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,220
No.

313
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:43,820
How come?

314
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:46,780
He took you here in person.

315
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:51,860
Zhang Chengzhao, Liang Huaiji,

316
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,140
go to the Cabinet

317
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:55,100
to give Prime Minister Wang the transcribed letter.

318
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:57,420
Hurry, he wants it now.

319
00:16:57,700 --> 00:16:58,580
- Yes, sir.- Yes, sir.

320
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:14,820
You little bastards!

321
00:17:14,820 --> 00:17:15,980
Are you blind?

322
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:19,540
It’s our fault

323
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,580
to get in your way.

324
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:23,380
Please forgive us.

325
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,860
We deserve to be punished.

326
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:40,340
We were walking straight

327
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,700
and they came out all of a sudden.

328
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:45,100
We could’ve been more cautious,

329
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:46,860
but they were more wrong.

330
00:17:47,340 --> 00:17:48,340
Why do you...

331
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:07,380
His Majesty

332
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,780
insisted to promote me,

333
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,700
and denied

334
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:11,900
all officials’ advice,

335
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:13,580
which caused their dissatisfaction.

336
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:16,380
Now that I only gave him a daughter,

337
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:18,060
the promotion

338
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:20,420
seemed to be extremely unnecessary.

339
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:25,300
Censors always need to give advice on something.

340
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,380
Now they are going on and on about this,

341
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:28,540
but with time,

342
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:30,020
when they realize you make no mistakes,

343
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:31,500
things will cool down.

344
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,940
But His Majesty must feel annoyed.

345
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:37,580
He’s been up against officials about this,

346
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:38,900
so naturally he becomes more sensitive.

347
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,540
You are his dearest family in his heart,

348
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:43,380
so he can only vent on you.

349
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:45,260
You must understand him.

350
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:48,220
I want him

351
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,540
to vent on me.

352
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:51,100
Being criticized by him is nothing to me.

353
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:54,580
I am worried

354
00:18:54,580 --> 00:18:56,500
officials are too hard on him.

355
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,900
That’s because His Majesty is kind-hearted.

356
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:01,300
He believes

357
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:04,380
only when voice can be heard
can the court be clear and transparent.

358
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:06,420
So he’s being very tolerant to officials.

359
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:07,780
Sometimes

360
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:10,220
they go a bit too far.

361
00:19:11,060 --> 00:19:13,060
When I was young, I always heard storytellers

362
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:15,940
describing the emperors as imposing persons,

363
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:17,540
if the officials

364
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:19,100
oppose what he wants to do,

365
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:20,100
he’ll just kill them.

366
00:19:20,460 --> 00:19:23,180
Why is His Majesty always bullied by them?

367
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:26,900
They are indeed too harsh on His Majesty.

368
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,060
Wherever there’s a disaster,

369
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:30,780
His Majesty would be so worried
about the people there

370
00:19:30,780 --> 00:19:32,580
that he can’t even eat anything.

371
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:34,540
But they will just write proposals the other day

372
00:19:34,860 --> 00:19:35,940
suspecting it is a warning from the Heaven

373
00:19:35,940 --> 00:19:37,540
to His Majesty

374
00:19:37,740 --> 00:19:39,140
for having too much enjoyment

375
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:40,820
in the palace.

376
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:43,300
They are not sensible.

377
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:46,340
They blame His Majesty
for not having many children,

378
00:19:46,740 --> 00:19:48,700
and on the other hand,
they want His Majesty to be ascetic.

379
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:55,620
I just feel sad for His Majesty.

380
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:58,820
They keep nagging

381
00:19:58,820 --> 00:20:00,340
about His Majesty’s family business.

382
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:02,140
Even if they

383
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:03,700
or any ordinary people

384
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:05,860
would feel angry

385
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:07,980
about this.

386
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:12,060
But

387
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:15,340
they only care and rebuke

388
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:18,020
His Majesty’s family business.

389
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:21,780
If it’s a butcher

390
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:22,700
or a tailor,

391
00:20:22,740 --> 00:20:24,300
no one would care if he has a son

392
00:20:24,580 --> 00:20:25,460
or

393
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:27,220
which girl he fell in love with.

394
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:10,740
You are here.

395
00:21:13,260 --> 00:21:15,420
My sister-in-law came to the palace the other day,

396
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:17,020
and brought me some fresh deer meat

397
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:17,980
hunted by my brother.

398
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:22,220
I remember

399
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:24,340
you mentioned you wanted to have
some dried deer meat.

400
00:21:24,860 --> 00:21:26,780
So yesterday I salted them early in the morning,

401
00:21:27,260 --> 00:21:28,460
and baked them this morning.

402
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:31,060
I also made some Moyao

403
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:32,860
and today it’s ready.

404
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,580
I just took it out and heated it up.

405
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:36,380
Would you like

406
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:37,420
to have some wine in the Hall of Peace?

407
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:42,380
And by the time

408
00:21:43,140 --> 00:21:44,700
you have a cup or two,

409
00:21:45,140 --> 00:21:46,740
the dried meat should be ready too.

410
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,500
You know

411
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:54,620
I’m annoyed by all the proposals

412
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:57,940
forcing me to pick a royal son.

413
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,780
You just want to know

414
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:04,340
if I’m going to take their proposal

415
00:22:04,340 --> 00:22:05,780
and pick a royal son.

416
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:10,140
I always talk to you about things happened
at the court,

417
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:12,140
and it’s something related to the harem.

418
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:14,620
Just ask what you want to know.

419
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:17,900
Don’t use such things

420
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,660
as excuses.

421
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:27,060
I do know

422
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:28,860
officials are asking Your Majesty

423
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:30,860
to adopt a royal son,

424
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:33,460
and I know you are annoyed by this.

425
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:36,620
That’s why I want to

426
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:40,260
invite you

427
00:22:40,260 --> 00:22:41,580
to have a drink in my place,

428
00:22:43,380 --> 00:22:45,300
not because I want to know

429
00:22:45,380 --> 00:22:47,100
if you’re going to take their proposal

430
00:22:48,020 --> 00:22:49,900
nor I want to

431
00:22:50,140 --> 00:22:51,860
adopt any royal son

432
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:52,740
to manipulate Your Majesty.

433
00:22:58,180 --> 00:22:59,260
Then why are you here?

434
00:23:01,620 --> 00:23:02,460
Why?

435
00:23:07,260 --> 00:23:07,980
Your Majesty,

436
00:23:07,980 --> 00:23:09,300
who am I to you?

437
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:16,540
Ever since you became the Empress,

438
00:23:17,260 --> 00:23:18,580
have I ever shown

439
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:20,460
any disrespect to your dignity as an empress?

440
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:23,660
Empress’ dignity?

441
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:31,820
Yes, the dignity.

442
00:23:35,220 --> 00:23:35,900
No, you haven’t.

443
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:39,860
You never hurt the Empress’ dignity.

444
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:44,100
You chose me to be the Empress,

445
00:23:44,220 --> 00:23:45,700
because it is the right thing to do.

446
00:23:46,940 --> 00:23:48,180
It’s the right choice for the court

447
00:23:48,180 --> 00:23:49,340
and the country.

448
00:23:50,860 --> 00:23:51,820
You need someone like me

449
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:53,180
to be the Empress

450
00:23:53,260 --> 00:23:54,460
to lead the harem,

451
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,740
but not

452
00:23:56,740 --> 00:23:57,940
your wife.

453
00:24:09,220 --> 00:24:10,060
I misbehaved.

454
00:24:10,060 --> 00:24:13,020
I’ll go back to reflect on myself

455
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,140
waiting for your punishment.

456
00:24:38,340 --> 00:24:39,060
Your Majesty,

457
00:24:42,260 --> 00:24:43,340
dinner is ready.

458
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:51,260
I lose my appetite.

459
00:24:53,740 --> 00:24:54,780
I’ll have a walk.

460
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:46,100
♪ The flowers are delicate in the moonlight ♪

461
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:55,180
♪ And I’ll meet you this night ♪

462
00:25:57,140 --> 00:26:05,500
♪ I stepped up stairs with golden shoes
in my hand ♪

463
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:15,140
♪ I finally saw you and snuggled in your arms ♪

464
00:26:18,140 --> 00:26:27,260
♪ I want you to give me all your love ♪

465
00:26:28,620 --> 00:26:29,820
When is it now?

466
00:26:29,820 --> 00:26:31,180
Can’t you restrain yourself?

467
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:36,340
= Instructor, Jia Yulan =
How many times have I told you?

468
00:26:37,340 --> 00:26:38,220
Once you are in the palace,

469
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:40,140
you must follow the rules in the palace.

470
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,500
One tiny mistake

471
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,940
can cost your life.

472
00:26:45,780 --> 00:26:46,580
Ms. Jia,

473
00:26:47,540 --> 00:26:48,860
the institute is occupied by the lads

474
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:50,660
to learn dance.

475
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:51,820
We have nowhere to go.

476
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:54,140
It has enough space here

477
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:54,900
and won’t disturb

478
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:55,900
any madam.

479
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,460
We were practicing the dance on the banquet,

480
00:26:58,060 --> 00:26:59,380
why are you criticizing us?

481
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:02,420
How dare you talk me back!

482
00:27:03,540 --> 00:27:04,980
Practicing the dance doesn’t matter,

483
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:06,820
but what were you singing just now?

484
00:27:07,420 --> 00:27:08,940
Are you going to sing it in the banquet?

485
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,500
What bullshit is that?

486
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,540
That song

487
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:13,860
sounds frivolous.

488
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:16,100
If some manager in the palace

489
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:17,140
hears of this,

490
00:27:17,620 --> 00:27:18,980
he’ll send you out after beating you.

491
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:20,540
Seriously, leave.

492
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:23,260
This is not for the banquet.

493
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:25,500
We were about to leave.

494
00:27:26,020 --> 00:27:27,260
I just wanted to train my voice

495
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:28,300
and sing a random song.

496
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:29,820
Don’t be angry, Ms. Jia.

497
00:27:30,140 --> 00:27:31,500
= Zhang Bihan =
Bihan doesn’t know

498
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:32,540
what the song and lyrics exactly mean.

499
00:27:32,780 --> 00:27:33,620
I just know

500
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,260
it’s written

501
00:27:34,260 --> 00:27:35,660
by a talented emperor.

502
00:27:36,300 --> 00:27:37,780
I didn’t know it’s a frivolous song.

503
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,020
Alright,

504
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:39,900
don’t say this bullshit

505
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:40,660
to me.

506
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:41,940
Go.

507
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,580
Your Majesty.

508
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:54,660
I’m the Instructor Jia Yulan,

509
00:27:55,380 --> 00:27:56,380
Your Majesty.

510
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,820
I don’t know you would be here.

511
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:02,740
I didn’t manage

512
00:28:02,740 --> 00:28:03,740
those girls well.

513
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:05,340
If they disturbed you,

514
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:06,820
please punish us.

515
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:08,860
You were here before I came.

516
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:11,060
I was just having a walk

517
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:12,740
and scared you.

518
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:16,980
Girls were having extra practice

519
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:18,020
for the important business.

520
00:28:18,660 --> 00:28:19,740
They are young

521
00:28:19,980 --> 00:28:21,100
and wanted to have some fun.

522
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:22,420
It’s not a big deal.

523
00:28:22,820 --> 00:28:24,020
Don’t punish them.

524
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:26,020
Merciful, Your Majesty.

525
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:32,620
Bihan,

526
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:35,700
His Majesty excused for you,

527
00:28:35,700 --> 00:28:36,820
come and thank him.

528
00:28:38,980 --> 00:28:39,860
Come.

529
00:28:41,620 --> 00:28:42,740
I met Your Majesty before.

530
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:54,340
You shouldn’t have.

531
00:28:56,340 --> 00:28:57,580
I did meet Your Majesty.

532
00:28:58,100 --> 00:28:59,180
I was only 10 years old

533
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:00,140
and this tall.

534
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:09,580
Master.

535
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:11,340
His Majesty summoned me?

536
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:12,060
His Majesty condemned Her Highness

537
00:29:12,100 --> 00:29:13,100
out of his anger

538
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:14,220
caused by officials’ proposals.

539
00:29:14,620 --> 00:29:15,460
Her Highness said

540
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,460
to wait for the punishment in her hall

541
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:17,180
and left.

542
00:29:17,460 --> 00:29:18,460
His Majesty became more angry

543
00:29:18,460 --> 00:29:19,340
and went away

544
00:29:19,340 --> 00:29:20,300
alone.

545
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:30,420
Master, where are you going?

546
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:36,260
At that time, my white rabbit

547
00:29:36,260 --> 00:29:37,340
was killed by a mouse,

548
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:39,460
I was chasing after it and saw you.

549
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:41,180
I didn’t know until today

550
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:42,100
that it was Your Majesty.

551
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:43,020
I

552
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:46,100
felt sleepy after I ate,

553
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:47,460
and had a dream

554
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:49,180
of you giving me another rabbit.

555
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:51,540
But when I woke up,

556
00:29:51,540 --> 00:29:52,660
Your Majesty was gone.

557
00:29:53,540 --> 00:29:54,580
I thought

558
00:29:54,620 --> 00:29:55,860
you were some imperial bodyguard

559
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:57,940
and tried to find you,

560
00:29:58,700 --> 00:29:59,540
but I couldn’t.

561
00:30:01,740 --> 00:30:02,700
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

562
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:03,420
Then I thought

563
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:07,140
you were some eunuch.

564
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:14,580
Your Majesty,

565
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,540
can you remember?

566
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,740
You are mistaken.

567
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:38,780
It’s late

568
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:40,540
and cold outside.

569
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:48,580
You’re wearing thin.

570
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:51,620
Go back to the institute.

571
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:55,740
The instructor has been waiting for you.

572
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:03,580
Have a rest, Your Majesty.

573
00:31:20,180 --> 00:31:21,060
You’re mistaken.

574
00:31:21,340 --> 00:31:22,300
Let’s go back.

575
00:31:25,860 --> 00:31:26,900
It’s impossible.

576
00:31:26,900 --> 00:31:27,660
I...

577
00:31:28,620 --> 00:31:29,300
I painted him repeatedly everyday

578
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:30,380
so that

579
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:32,140
I would not forget him.

580
00:31:32,740 --> 00:31:33,340
Ms. Jia,

581
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,180
do you remember you asked me before

582
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:37,740
you gave me more allowance

583
00:31:38,260 --> 00:31:39,180
than others, but

584
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:41,020
why I didn’t have more jewelry than others

585
00:31:41,380 --> 00:31:42,860
or saved any money.

586
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:43,600
That,

587
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:44,300
that is because

588
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,740
I spent all my money on drawing papers and colors.

589
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:50,380
But you were young.

590
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:52,180
Maybe you remembered wrongly.

591
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:53,380
No, it’s impossible.

592
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:56,140
Alright,

593
00:31:56,500 --> 00:31:58,020
impossible or not,

594
00:31:58,940 --> 00:31:59,780
I think...

595
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,460
I think His Majesty likes you.

596
00:32:04,260 --> 00:32:04,980
See?

597
00:32:08,460 --> 00:32:09,540
How can you know?

598
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,380
If he really likes you,

599
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:12,900
why can’t he remember?

600
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:16,300
Just do what I tell you to do.

601
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:18,180
I will let him remember

602
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:21,060
who you are.

603
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:27,820
Alright, don’t think too much.

604
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:34,060
I know you

605
00:32:35,020 --> 00:32:36,340
are a lucky girl.

606
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:41,180
I’m right.

607
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:44,900
You deserve all the love I gave you.

608
00:33:18,940 --> 00:33:19,420
Your Highness,

609
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:21,020
the dried meat is done.

610
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,420
It’s the right time.

611
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:29,900
You cut, seasoned

612
00:33:30,540 --> 00:33:31,820
and salted it early in the morning.

613
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:37,140
Send them

614
00:33:39,220 --> 00:33:40,660
to the madams.

615
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:43,660
But,

616
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:46,540
but you said…

617
00:33:47,780 --> 00:33:48,780
I remembered wrongly.

618
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:53,060
His Majesty doesn’t like the dried deer meat.

619
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:05,540
Your Highness,

620
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:07,100
Mr. Zhang Maoze is here.

621
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:16,420
Your Highness,

622
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:26,620
I wanted to ask you something.

623
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:28,260
Before His Majesty said

624
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:30,260
he wanted to arrange a eunuch

625
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:31,220
and two maids for the Hall of Phoenix.

626
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:32,500
They must be young

627
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:35,300
so that they can accompany the princess.

628
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:39,860
This can wait.

629
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:45,460
The wet nurse and nanny for the princess

630
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:46,580
have been selected

631
00:34:46,820 --> 00:34:48,460
by Officer Ren.

632
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:50,060
But selecting

633
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:52,220
eunuchs and maids

634
00:34:52,220 --> 00:34:53,060
to play with the princess

635
00:34:53,140 --> 00:34:54,260
is not a convention.

636
00:34:54,980 --> 00:34:56,780
It is not a big thing,

637
00:34:57,540 --> 00:34:59,140
and His Majesty asked for it.

638
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:04,140
The court is watching at the Pavilion of Phoenix.

639
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:07,380
They don’t even need to break any law
or regulation,

640
00:35:10,500 --> 00:35:13,300
as long as there’s anything against
the conventions,

641
00:35:14,620 --> 00:35:16,980
proposals

642
00:35:17,460 --> 00:35:19,300
will cover His Majesty’s desk.

643
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:25,620
Few years later I’ll adopt

644
00:35:26,140 --> 00:35:27,540
some girl from a good family.

645
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,660
Once she’s in the palace,

646
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:34,580
we’ll assign their servants.

647
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,220
But

648
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:40,500
His Majesty

649
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:42,180
has been pushed so hard by officials.

650
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:43,460
He’s not in a good mood

651
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:44,980
and might...

652
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:54,020
He might vent on me?

653
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:00,060
No,

654
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:03,460
not just vent on me,

655
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:09,180
he would suspect I have my personal intention.

656
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:10,980
Your Highness.

657
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,940
You came from the Hall of
Happiness and Tranquility right?

658
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:22,020
You came here at late night

659
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:26,180
not because you have something urgent to tell,

660
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:29,300
but because you knew His Majesty condemned me

661
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:33,340
and wanted to tell me

662
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:38,020
not to misunderstand His Majesty.

663
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:42,820
No,

664
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:46,380
I didn’t misunderstand His Majesty.

665
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:50,020
I am not angry at him, either.

666
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:55,620
I just feel sad for him.

667
00:36:58,700 --> 00:36:59,940
His Majesty is in misery.

668
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:03,740
When he’s restrained by others,

669
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:06,860
he had to

670
00:37:08,500 --> 00:37:09,420
take women he doesn’t like

671
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,980
to the palace

672
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,380
to be his wife

673
00:37:14,020 --> 00:37:15,180
and the mother of this nation

674
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:17,740
for the stability of the court.

675
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:23,460
Now his willfulness

676
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:26,220
is just because

677
00:37:26,220 --> 00:37:27,740
the woman he married for this country

678
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,700
is just the Empress

679
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:36,900
not his wife.

680
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:44,820
He only sees Madam Miao as his wife,

681
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:46,660
doesn’t he, Pingfu?

682
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,380
In all these years,

683
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:55,220
has he slept in

684
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:59,700
any palace other than the Pavilion of Phoenix?

685
00:38:06,740 --> 00:38:09,460
His Majesty always read proposals

686
00:38:09,980 --> 00:38:11,500
and classics till late night.

687
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:17,860
Now,

688
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,900
the woman he acknowledged in his heart

689
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:25,540
finally made him a father,

690
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:29,620
yet officials at court

691
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:33,260
don’t care about

692
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:35,060
his daughter,

693
00:38:37,140 --> 00:38:39,860
but want to give him a royal child

694
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,780
to be his son.

695
00:38:45,180 --> 00:38:46,180
In this way

696
00:38:49,620 --> 00:38:51,300
I am luckier than him.

697
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,820
Because at least

698
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:01,260
I married the man

699
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:03,300
I love with all my life.

700
00:39:19,020 --> 00:39:20,260
You came here to announce

701
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:25,020
any imperial edict?

702
00:39:27,580 --> 00:39:28,540
No.

703
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:31,340
I heard

704
00:39:31,860 --> 00:39:33,140
you were wronged.

705
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,020
I couldn’t help

706
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:37,660
coming to visit you.

707
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:47,020
Every time when I have difficulties,

708
00:39:49,500 --> 00:39:52,100
you are accompanying me.

709
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:54,660
Thank you so much.

710
00:39:58,500 --> 00:40:00,380
Maybe it’s the destiny.

711
00:40:01,060 --> 00:40:01,980
You are meant to

712
00:40:01,980 --> 00:40:03,740
the woman who accompanies and assists His Majesty,

713
00:40:04,220 --> 00:40:05,580
and the Empress

714
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,620
I’m loyal to in my life.

715
00:40:07,740 --> 00:40:09,740
That’s why the Heaven sent me

716
00:40:09,740 --> 00:40:11,780
to Your Highness at the countryside

717
00:40:12,300 --> 00:40:14,660
and helped you out of the trouble.

718
00:40:18,820 --> 00:40:19,620
Meant to be?

719
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:25,620
Since the wedding night of
Your Highness with His Majesty,

720
00:40:26,020 --> 00:40:27,020
I knew

721
00:40:27,420 --> 00:40:29,460
you are his destined wife.

722
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:49,500
That day,

723
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:52,060
you threw it to the fire pot,

724
00:40:52,580 --> 00:40:55,060
but next morning when I cleaned the fire pot,

725
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:58,140
I found it’s dropped out of the pot

726
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:00,540
and not damaged even a little.

727
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:03,420
This is the will of the Heaven.

728
00:42:08,700 --> 00:42:11,060
= Be cautious, be restrained =

729
00:42:38,820 --> 00:42:39,580
Liaozi.

730
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:42,660
Your Majesty.

731
00:42:44,300 --> 00:42:45,180
Check the record.

732
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:47,500
Find all the ladies of county

733
00:42:48,220 --> 00:42:49,260
that I never summoned.

734
00:42:49,420 --> 00:42:50,300
Call them to serve me.

735
00:42:51,460 --> 00:42:52,380
From now on,

736
00:42:53,260 --> 00:42:55,140
summon a lady every ten days

737
00:42:55,140 --> 00:42:56,220
to serve me in the Hall of Happiness
and Tranquility.

738
00:42:58,420 --> 00:42:59,300
I’ll do it right now.

739
00:43:01,260 --> 00:43:02,860
Have some warm soup.

740
00:43:07,540 --> 00:43:09,060
All previous tonics

741
00:43:09,140 --> 00:43:10,700
that I used to refuse to take

742
00:43:11,260 --> 00:43:13,220
because they are disgusting,

743
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:16,780
serve them every other day.

744
00:43:26,060 --> 00:43:35,740
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

745
00:43:37,060 --> 00:43:45,420
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

746
00:43:48,260 --> 00:43:52,980
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

747
00:43:53,940 --> 00:43:58,100
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

748
00:43:59,540 --> 00:44:05,020
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

749
00:44:05,020 --> 00:44:09,820
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

750
00:44:13,500 --> 00:44:19,140
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

751
00:44:19,140 --> 00:44:24,020
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

752
00:44:24,540 --> 00:44:30,300
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

753
00:44:30,300 --> 00:44:35,380
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

754
00:44:35,820 --> 00:44:40,740
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

755
00:44:41,380 --> 00:44:46,220
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

756
00:44:46,900 --> 00:44:52,060
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

757
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:57,580
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

758
00:44:58,140 --> 00:45:02,220
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

759
00:45:03,660 --> 00:45:08,300
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

760
00:45:09,340 --> 00:45:14,500
♪ The howling wind ♪

761
00:45:14,860 --> 00:45:18,940
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

762
00:45:20,420 --> 00:45:25,340
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

763
00:45:25,980 --> 00:45:31,220
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

764
00:45:31,620 --> 00:45:36,900
♪ The howling wind ♪

765
00:45:37,220 --> 00:45:42,100
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

766
00:45:42,700 --> 00:45:49,420
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
